snippet.title: De La Jet Set Radio (Jet Grind Radio) LongPlay (English) (Sega Dreamcast) (No Commentary) (1080P HD)
snippet.description:
This is a longplay of De La Jet Set Radio recorded on A VA1 Sega Dreamcast equipped with a DCDigital. 
This is De La Jet Set Radio; The final version of the original game only released in Japan through the now long defunct Sega Direct Store in 2001 which combines the NTSC and PAL version exclusive content together with some of the original Japanese audio for the "Definitive" version. The entire game is in English otherwise.
